AFROCENTRIC BAYITH YAHWEH YAHDAIM AFRICAN HEBREWS, INC. and Ben Yahweh Abiyah-Mosheh, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DESOTO CORRECTIONAL INSTITUTION, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3311 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 17, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed because of the appellants' failure to satisfy this court's August 20, 2018 fee order.

KHOUZAM, ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
